{"tid":1530490,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"我再重申一次 影響你升學既只有DSE成績","createTime":"2019-09-02T03:28:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T11:39:55.000Z","uid":190141,"like":59,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f7462c666e126d75d18d30440643b29204e8ebed","tid":1530490,"uid":190141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:28:03.000Z","msg":"乜撚野大過小過缺點全部無撚用無影響架 JUPAS淨係睇你張DSE成績表考幾多分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你唔會話因為好撚多優點 20分都入到神科<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亦都唔會因為好撚多缺點 7科5**都入唔到神科<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">D缺點大小過係用黎嚇人 唔撚洗理架</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中學手足們 放心放膽去做D自己覺得岩既事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"518771587ca0697521af2d9e4ada2155e823df38","tid":1530490,"uid":211537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:28:44.000Z","msg":"Psuh"},{"pid":"52cfc8884bd3b0c572d87df2b197e5ce3465b622","tid":1530490,"uid":7948,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:29:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ALupoHa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FALupoHa.jpg&h=b51370df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15e8b6df74c49cd4ad99d0bb1811ef83d3ee990b","tid":1530490,"uid":63461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:29:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0f6b9acfc4f2c55774d708758d4f18161cfd2c0","tid":1530490,"uid":190141,"like":6,"dislike":1,"sc